summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting the condemnation award In The Matter of The Petition Of The City Of Seattle to acquire by condemnation certain property and property rights required for North 85th Street, Urban Arterial Board project, as authorized by Ordinance 113098, King County Cause No. 87-2-01730-3, and authorizing payment. (North 85th Street UAB; RW 8607-3).
